fi.lrkr.pathfinder.vertex

Class Node

  • java.lang.Object
    • fi.lrkr.pathfinder.vertex.Node
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Vertex, java.lang.Comparable<Node>

    public class Node
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Comparable<Node>, Vertex
    Class provides representation of a node in a Maze (or any graph). It has a Location for Maze coordinates, length from the start and heuristic score to the end.
